<div id="Idea_2526"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2526-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2526">Create a grant program for non-profits run by former officials.  &nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">kbaegis</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Having spoken to people in public office during the Bush administration who resigned for ethical reasons, they were by far the most qualified individuals to voice concerns and protest.  Recognizing these people as the best people to add to the public discussion as well as the most likely individuals to form new national and grassroots organizations around real issues, I propose the creation of federal grant programs to fund non-profits organized or run by former state officials.  </div>
